{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/uBlock-origin-1p-filters/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Traverse"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"84999286-8a93-5463-889d-feb02e8005ce","excerpt":"uBlock Origin 已經是裝 Chrome 系瀏覽器必備擴充程式 預設功能已經可以阻擋多種網頁廣告和 youtube 影片廣告 還可以安裝第三方提供的 AdBlock list 像是 EasyList、AdGuard Filters…","html":"<p><a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ublock-origin/cjpalhdlnbpafiamejdnhcphjbkeiagm?utm_source=app-launcher\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">uBlock Origin</a> 已經是裝 Chrome 系瀏覽器必備擴充程式</p>\n<p>預設功能已經可以阻擋多種網頁廣告和 youtube 影片廣告</p>\n<p>還可以安裝第三方提供的 AdBlock list</p>\n<p>像是 <a href=\"https://easylist.to/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">EasyList</a>、<a href=\"https://adguard.com/kb/general/ad-filtering/adguard-filters/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">AdGuard Filters</a>…等</p>\n<p>更加分的是可以「自訂靜態過濾規格」隱藏特定網頁不想看到的區塊</p>\n<p>如現在 youtube 首頁也有短影片</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 76.66666666666666%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Youtube Shorts\"\n        title=\"Youtube Shorts\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/80e3c/youtube-shorts.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/4ec73/youtube-shorts.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/158ba/youtube-shorts.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/80e3c/youtube-shorts.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/47311/youtube-shorts.jpg 1080w,\n/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/644c5/youtube-shorts.jpg 1440w,\n/traverse/static/ab552ce0d54105edc457622bbf1e5f45/61936/youtube-shorts.jpg 3064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>從工具列點 uBlock 圖示右下角打開控制台到「自訂靜態過濾規格」</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 81.66666666666667%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Open dashbaord\"\n        title=\"Open dashbaord\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/80e3c/open-dashboard.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/4ec73/open-dashboard.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/158ba/open-dashboard.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/80e3c/open-dashboard.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/47311/open-dashboard.jpg 1080w,\n/traverse/static/c8fe88b02fbef770dcf1b31894e79b99/45687/open-dashboard.jpg 1262w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>輸入下面規則可以隱藏首頁 Shorts 區塊</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"txt\"><pre class=\"language-txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">www.youtube.com##ytd-rich-section-renderer.ytd-rich-grid-renderer:has-text(shorts)</code></pre></div>\n<p>再輸入下面規則可以隱藏 Youtube 導航 Shorts 入口</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"txt\"><pre class=\"language-txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">www.youtube.com##ytd-guide-entry-renderer.ytd-guide-section-renderer:has(a[title=\"Shorts\"])\nwww.youtube.com##ytd-mini-guide-entry-renderer.ytd-mini-guide-renderer:has(a[title=\"Shorts\"])</code></pre></div>\n<p>這下 Youtube 首頁清爽多了</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 720px; margin: initial;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.55555555555556%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Youtube Home\"\n        title=\"Youtube Home\"\n        src=\"/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/80e3c/youtube-home.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/4ec73/youtube-home.jpg 180w,\n/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/158ba/youtube-home.jpg 360w,\n/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/80e3c/youtube-home.jpg 720w,\n/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/47311/youtube-home.jpg 1080w,\n/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/644c5/youtube-home.jpg 1440w,\n/traverse/static/f6d40ee9d73301d1f4b99d9840ad941f/61936/youtube-home.jpg 3064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n        decoding=\"async\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>更多自訂規則說明參考 <a href=\"https://github.com/gorhill/uBlock/wiki/Procedural-cosmetic-filters\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Procedural cosmetic filters · gorhill/uBlock Wiki</a></p>","frontmatter":{